// Git hard clean

git reset --hard FETCH_HEAD

// delete untracked files
git clean -df   

/delete commits not pushed to remote
git reset --hard origin/<branch_name>




//=============CMD===============
Kill task in windows from cmd
>tasklist

>taskkill /PID <processId> /f    // forced kill
or
>taskkill /IM <processName> /f


Install nvm (Node Version Manager) - to switch between node versions as per compatibility
command
nvm ls -> current node version used
nvm use 8.11  -> use specified node version (but that version should be installed)




VisualStudio Cheat

customise using settings.json file

To open open file in new table go to settings.json (a vs code settings file)
"workbench.editor.enablePreview": false

Ctrl + K/enter 		: to keep tab open
"workbench.editor.enablePreview": false settings.json (a vs code settings file)

In latest version of VScode
navigation Ctrl+clik doesn't work -settings.json 
users settings
remove "editor.multiCursorModifier": "ctrlCmd"



